{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"@objc","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"dynamic","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"isEnergySavingEnabled","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Bool","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" { ","kind":"text"},{"text":"get","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"set","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" }","kind":"text"}],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration\/isEnergySavingEnabled","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"sections":[],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/scanbotdocumentscannersdk\/sbsdkbasescannerenergyconfiguration\/isenergysavingenabled"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]},{"paths":["\/documentation\/scanbotdocumentscannersdk\/sbsdkbasescannerenergyconfiguration\/isenergysavingenabled"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Set to "},{"code":"true","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", if automatic energy saving should be enabled. With automatic energy saving enabled the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"base scanner view controller will, after a certain time of inactivity, enter the energy save mode by lowering the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"detection\/scanning rate."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Defaults to "},{"code":"true","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"metadata":{"externalID":"c:@M@ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK@objc(cs)SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration(py)isEnergySavingEnabled","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"isEnergySavingEnabled"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb","text":"Bool"}],"symbolKind":"property","role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Instance Property","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"isEnergySavingEnabled"}],"title":"isEnergySavingEnabled","modules":[{"name":"ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK"}]},"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK","doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration"]]},"references":{"doc://net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK/documentation/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration":{"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration"}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration"}],"url":"\/documentation\/scanbotdocumentscannersdk\/sbsdkbasescannerenergyconfiguration","title":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"The energy management configuration object for a ‘SBSDKBaseScannerViewController’ and its subclasses.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"‘SBSDKBaseScannerViewController’ and subclasses sport a customizable energy management system.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Since scanners running on a live video feed can put a lot of load onto the CPU and\/or GPU","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"of the device, causing the battery to drain quickly and running the device hot, you can customize the energy","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"consumption using this class by configuring the rate of detections\/recognitions per second in performance mode as","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"well as in energy saving mode.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"In performance mode the scanners will be fed with a higher, configurable rate of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"video frames per second.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"After a certain, configurable period of inactivity the energy save mode will be engaged and the rate","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"of scans will be reduced to a lower (configurable) rate.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"You can also configure the time of inactivity before the automatic mode switches from performance to energy save mode.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Inactivity here means that both of the following conditions are met:","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration"},"doc://net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK/documentation/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK":{"url":"\/documentation\/scanbotdocumentscannersdk","title":"ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Version: 8.0.3"}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK","kind":"symbol","role":"collection"},"doc://net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK/documentation/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration/isEnergySavingEnabled":{"url":"\/documentation\/scanbotdocumentscannersdk\/sbsdkbasescannerenergyconfiguration\/isenergysavingenabled","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"Set to ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"true"},{"text":", if automatic energy saving should be enabled. With automatic energy saving enabled the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"base scanner view controller will, after a certain time of inactivity, enter the energy save mode by lowering the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"detection\/scanning rate.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Defaults to ","type":"text"},{"code":"true","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration\/isEnergySavingEnabled","title":"isEnergySavingEnabled","fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"isEnergySavingEnabled","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb","text":"Bool","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"isEnergySavingEnabled","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol"}},"variantOverrides":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"patch":[{"path":"\/identifier\/interfaceLanguage","op":"replace","value":"occ"},{"path":"\/metadata\/roleHeading","op":"replace","value":"Instance Property"},{"path":"\/metadata\/title","op":"replace","value":"isEnergySavingEnabled"},{"path":"\/metadata\/symbolKind","op":"replace","value":"property"},{"path":"\/metadata\/fragments","op":"replace","value":[{"text":"isEnergySavingEnabled","kind":"identifier"}]},{"path":"\/topicSections","op":"add","value":null},{"path":"\/relationshipsSections","op":"add","value":null},{"path":"\/seeAlsoSections","op":"add","value":null},{"path":"\/primaryContentSections\/0","op":"replace","value":{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"nonatomic"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL","text":"BOOL"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"isEnergySavingEnabled"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"]}]}},{"path":"\/references\/doc:~1~1net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK~1documentation~1ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK~1SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration\/title","op":"replace","value":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration"},{"path":"\/references\/doc:~1~1net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK~1documentation~1ScanbotDoc